{"tid":776173,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高圖爾斯為當年辱罵皇馬一事道歉","createTime":"2018-08-11T19:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T19:14:40.000Z","uid":20634,"like":14,"dislike":118,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"798e87be5c9e97b45db1f522ed3fba5706d41440","tid":776173,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T19:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/08/10/a/a52e56ac16c27af55dfaf0f42b311497.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2Fa%2Fa52e56ac16c27af55dfaf0f42b311497.jpg&h=00208c44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　在加盟皇馬的亮相儀式上，高圖爾斯多次親吻皇馬波衫上的會徽，他表示這是他第一次親吻一傢俱樂部的會徽，這證明了他對皇馬的愛。<br />\n<br />\n　　高圖爾斯表示，自己有一個「兒皇夢」，而他的偶像是卡斯拿斯。在他小的時候，因為皇馬和安德列治隊有一場比賽，他父親的朋友送給了他一件卡斯拿斯的波衫。<span style=\"color: red;\">正是從那時起，他喜歡上了皇馬。</span><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　「他那麼年輕就那麼沉穩，當時他只有18歲，他的反應令人印象深刻。一開始最吸引我注意的，是一位18歲的門將就能在班拿貝巨大的壓力下為皇馬守門，因為這必須做到精神非常強大。」<br />\n<br />\n　　在為馬體會效力時，高圖爾斯曾帶領馬體會球員諷刺皇馬，高唱「X翻皇馬人」，對此高圖爾斯表示了道歉：「那時我年輕，如果有人感覺受到了冒犯，那我表示道歉。」<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n　　而對於加盟皇馬，高圖爾斯表示，「今天我完成了一個夢想，你們無法想像我對到這裡來有多期待。加盟皇馬並不容易，這是我童年的夢想。我曾與皇馬當對手，知道對陣皇馬意味著什麼。今天我也是一個皇馬人了。」（沙治奧）"},{"pid":"196f28ae62d86523fa21f0b4d548b615979df23c","tid":776173,"uid":172376,"like":81,"dislike":2,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T19:09:41.000Z","msg":"25就25啦咁多嗲"},{"pid":"ef0f0260256fd28d535bd9b501614e2fc3b76d60","tid":776173,"uid":131369,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T19:33:08.000Z","msg":"好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ee6ef71455542c0e4c3485d9c72f0ed351c8f5","tid":776173,"uid":54431,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T19:34:27.000Z","msg":"好撚核凸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75d60fd73074a43d26615dc3d05418d306a6b43","tid":776173,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T19:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88422762e282045661020eb7453e5374ecd9a14","tid":776173,"uid":35070,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T20:37:45.000Z","msg":"似足香港偽人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81ad86910ba1b6b4c371b16cce200b8b1d34053","tid":776173,"uid":1346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T20:53:14.000Z","msg":"25仔收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef765c68f4580acc465196f973923ad9a7772d5","tid":776173,"uid":34419,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T01:54:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"> 加盟皇馬並不容易，這是我童年的夢想。我曾與皇馬當對手，知道對陣皇馬意味著什麼。今天我也是一個皇馬人了。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182db8c050d76a75e7259a3cff5e56774fabe5da","tid":776173,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:05:04.000Z","msg":"點解有主力唔做去做後備?"},{"pid":"b0bd30a685abeefd77a308381440a9932415a54e","tid":776173,"uid":53466,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e859dfb4b6e376316e4dee36f20d4a91c903acec","tid":776173,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"25"},{"pid":"d68c46db9588d15b57728b29a570aaf53dcd693c","tid":776173,"uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:10:23.000Z","msg":"呢個陷家產快撚d 出醜"},{"pid":"2857919af36e66a85d6b7d8411502ab642ef4bcd","tid":776173,"uid":155137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T02:10:57.000Z","msg":"聖卡西有咩下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bdb983d3ded8b429c10e5380d5d42a52e0dc69","tid